\begin_layout Abstract
This document defines protocols, procedures and conventions to be implemented
 by peers implementing the Generic Security Service Application Program
 Interface (GSS-API) when using the BrowserID authentication mechanism.
 Through the GS2 family of mechanisms defined in RFC 5801, these protocols
 also define how Simple Authentication and Security Layer (SASL, RFC 4422)
 applications may use BrowserID.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
